provisions of international telecommunications facilities last updated  thursday  november      this section ath strategiescorporate governanceownership structureboard  managementsponsorships main menu homeabout athath strategiescorporate governanceownership structureboard  managementsponsorshipsath groupsmediaannual reportcontact us search latest news media fnpfs latest pension reform projects  developments newsletter ath strategy aths values are integrity accountability innovation efficiency and effectiveness ath reports ath annual reports are eagerly waited upon by the community and government ath projects the ath vodafone foundation is bestowing its philanthropic responsibility on the community sitemap copyright   ath group of companies all rights reserved this site is powered by  amalgamated telecom holdings limited private company information  bloomberg august    am et diversified telecommunication services company overview of amalgamated telecom holdings limited snapshot people company overview amalgamated telecom holdings limited through its subsidiaries offers telecommunications and related services in fiji the company operates through three segments fixed line telecommunications fixed line telecom mobile telecommunications mobile telecom and other the fixed line telecom segment offers fixed line telecommunication services including the sale or lease of telecommunications related office equipment accessories and services such as prepaid telephony and card services the mobile telecom segment provides mobile telecommunication services comprising the sale of associated equipment accessories and services the other segment offers international public and dedicated t amalgamated telecom holdings limited through its subsidiaries offers telecommunications and related services in fiji the company operates through three segments fixed line telecommunications fixed line telecom mobile telecommunications mobile telecom and other the fixed line telecom segment offers fixed line telecommunication services including the sale or lease of telecommunications related office equipment accessories and services such as prepaid telephony and card services the mobile telecom segment provides mobile telecommunication services comprising the sale of associated equipment accessories and services the other segment offers international public and dedicated telecommunications data and internet services sells computer hardware and software and provides technical support and directory services it is also involved in the compilation and publication of the fiji telephone directory as well as provision of call center services the company was founded in  and is based in suva fiji amalgamated telecom holdings limited is a subsidiary of fiji national provident fund detailed description harbour front buildinglevel rodwell roadpo box suva  fijifounded in  phone    fax    wwwathcomfj key executives for amalgamated telecom holdings limited mr ivan fong ceo  company secretary mr kamlesh sharma chief executive officer of amalgamated telecom holdings kribati limited ms sisilia daveta acting manager of finance compensation as of fiscal year  amalgamated telecom holdings limited key developments amalgamated telecom holdings limited reports audited consolidated and parent earnings results for the year ended march   jun   amalgamated telecom holdings limited reported audited consolidated and parent earnings results for the year ended march   for the year on consolidated basis the company reported revenue was fjd  against fjd  a year ago operating profit was fjd  against fjd  a year ago profit from operations was fjd  compared to fjd  a year ago profit before income tax was  against fjd  a year ago profit attributable to equity holders of the holding company was fjd  against fjd  a year ago basic and diluted earnings per share were  cents against  cents a year ago net cash inflows from operating activities were fjd  against fjd  a year ago payments for property plant